LOCUS       sequence-476201-        4770 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  sgRNA cloning vector with EGFP expression cassette. An sgRNA spacer 
            sequence can be cloned into BbsI sites. A CMV-EGFP expression 
            cassette is included as a reporter of transfection efficiency..
